title: Ohio DevFest 2016 Summary
brief: Ohio DevFest 2016 is now over. It was a huge success. We are happy to share with you some facts, emotions and, of course, photos from the first Google Developers Conference in Ohio!

title: After Party at Zaftig!
brief: The fun isn't over just because the talks are finished! We're headed to Zaftig.

title: No better place to be Saturday Nov 18th!
brief: Just take a peek at all that is going on Satuday at Ohio DevFest.  There's no better place to be Saturday November 18th.
